    "If we give these raw numbers to our computer, it will get confused. Because the Parkinson's samples happened to have larger `Total_Reads` (total sequencing depth), their raw bacteria counts look really high across the board! \n",
    "\n",
    "Let's look at a **boxplot** of this raw data. A boxplot shows the spread of the data—the box is where most patients fall, and the lines show the extremes."
